utsche.de/sport/leichtathletik-berlin-klosterhalfen-stellt-deutschen-rekord-ueber-5000-meter-auf-dpa.urn-newsml-dpa-com-20090101-190803-99-327411|title=Klosterhalfen stellt deutschen Rekord \u00fcber 5000 Meter auf|last=Germany|first=S\u00fcddeutsche de GmbH, Munich|website=S\u00fcddeutsche.de|language=de|date=3 August 2019|access-date=3 August 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n!14\n|14:27.49\n|{{flagathlete|[[Margaret Kipkemboi]]|KEN}}\n|5 October 2019\n|Doha\n|<ref name=WC2019>{{cite web|title=5000m Women \u2212 Final \u2212 Results|url=https://media.aws.iaaf.org/competitiondocuments/pdf/6033/AT-5000-W-f----.RS6.pdf?v=-391446717|publisher=IAAF|date=5 October 2019|accessdate=6 October 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n!15\n|14:27.55\n|{{flagathlete|[[Caroline Chepkoech Kipkirui]]|KEN}}\n|1 September 2017\n|Brussels\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=5000m Results|url=http://static.sportresult.com/sports/at/data/2017/brussels/re1170040.pdf|work=sportresult.com|date=1 September 2017|accessdate=2 September 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n!16\n|14:28.09 ||{{flagathlete|[[Jiang Bo (athlete)|Jiang Bo]]|CHN}}|| 23 October 1997 ||[[Shanghai]]\n|-\n!17\n|14:28.39 ||{{flagathlete|[[Sentayehu Ejigu]]|ETH}}|| 16 July 2010 || Paris\n|-\n!18\n|14:29.11 ||{{flagathlete|[[Paula Radcliffe]]|GBR}}|| 20 June 2004 ||[[Bydgoszcz]]\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" |19\n| rowspan=\"2\" |14:29.32\n|{{flagathlete|[[Olga Yegorova]]|RUS}}|| 31 August 2001 || Berlin\n|-\n|{{flagathlete|[[Berhane Adere]]|ETH|1996}} || 27 June 2003 || [[Oslo]] \n|-\n!21\n|14:29.60\n|{{flagathlete|[[Tsehay Gemechu]]|ETH}}\n|5 October 2019\n|Doha\n|<ref name=WC2019/>\n|-\n!22\n|14:29.82\n|{{flagathlete|[[Dong Yanmei]]|CHN}}\n|23 October 1997\n|[[Shanghai]]\n| \n|-\n!23\n|14:30.42  || {{flagathlete|[[Sally Kipyego]]|KEN}} || 8 September 2011 || [[Z\u00fcrich]] \n|-\n!24\n|14:30.88  || {{flagathlete|[[Gete Wami]]|ETH|1996}} || 5 August 2000 || [[Heusden-Zolder]] \n|-\n!25\n|14:31.14  || {{flagathlete|[[Linet Chepkwemoi Masai]]|KEN}} || 23 May 2010 || Shanghai \n|}\n\n====Notes====\n