hletics (track and field)|1962]]\n|13:38.4\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|[[Murray Halberg]]|NZL}}\n|[[Auckland]]\n|-\n|[[1961 in athletics (track and field)|1961]]\n|13:38.2\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|[[Murray Halberg]]|NZL}}\n|[[Stockholm]]\n|-\n|[[1960 in athletics (track and field)|1960]]\n|13:38.1\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|[[Pyotr Bolotnikov]]|URS}}\n|[[Kiev]]\n|}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Women===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!Year\n!Time\n!Athlete\n!Location\n|-\n|[[2019 in athletics (track and field)|2019]]\n|14:20.36\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|[[Hellen Obiri]]|KEN}}\n|London\n|-\n|[[2018 in athletics (track and field)|2018]]\n|14:21.75\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|[[Hellen Obiri]]|KEN}}\n|[[Rabat]]\n|-\n|[[2017 in athletics (track and field)|2017]]\n|14:18.37\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|[[Hellen Obiri]]|KEN}}\n|[[Rome]]\n|-\n|[[2016 in athletics (track and field)|2016]]\n|14:12.59\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|[[Almaz Ayana]]|ETH}}\n|[[Stadio Olimpico|Rome]]\n|-\n|[[2015 in athletics (track and field)|2015]]\n|14:14.32\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|[[Almaz Ayana]]|ETH}}\n|[[Shanghai]]\n|-\n|[[2014 in athletics (track and field)|2014]]\n|14:28.88\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|[[Genzebe Dibaba]]|ETH}}\n|[[Monaco]]\n|-\n|[[2013 in athletics (track and field)|2013]]\n|14:23.68\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|[[Tirunesh Dibaba]]|ETH}}\n|[[Paris]]\n|-\n|[[2012 in athletics (track and field)|2012]]\n|14:35.62\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|[[Vivian Cheruiyot]]|KEN}}\n|[[Rome]]\n|-\n|[[2011 in athletics (track and field)|2011]]\n|14:20.87\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|[[Vivian Cheruiyot]]|KEN}}\n|[[Stockholm]]\n|-\n|[[2010 in athletics (track and field)|2010]]\n|14:24.79i\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|[[Meseret Defar]]|ETH}}\n|[[Stockholm]]\n|-\n|[[2009 in athletics (track and field)|2009]]\n|14:24.37i\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|[[Meseret Defar]]|ETH}}\n|[[Stockholm]]\n|-\n|[[2008 in athletics (track and field)|2008]]\n|14:11.15\n|align=left|{{flagathlete|[[Tirunesh 